Im the kind of person that hold my feelings back, so if im mad at someone, that someone would not know. Over march break i thought i would have the best time i took of work and my best friend did too. We spent everyday together, but by the end of march break i wanted to DIE. friends tend to tell you ur flaws over and over again. and over the march break i realized that i had flaws that i did not know about. My friend lets call her "Sue" complains that i tend to change when other ppl are around. maybe i do, but its because not alot of people know the real me. she got a new boyfriend and im happy for her, but guess whos the one who changes now. now she talks about me all the time to her new boyfriend and i hate that. and now that i told her that im fed up with that SHE IS MAD AT ME. who is wrong?
